00:33:49,841 --> 00:33:51,758
-I'm good at this. Come.
-It's impossible.

841
00:33:51,841 --> 00:33:53,038
Listen, I'll get it on my first try.

842
00:33:53,121 --> 00:33:54,318
You're just wasting your money.

843
00:33:54,401 --> 00:33:55,441
That's impossible. Look.

844
00:33:57,401 --> 00:33:58,441
Let me show you.

845
00:34:07,161 --> 00:34:08,161
Senior,

846
00:34:08,441 --> 00:34:10,401
I don't think I can do that.

847
00:34:11,201 --> 00:34:12,881
(You own many companies
in the tertiary industry.)

848
00:34:13,441 --> 00:34:15,720
Is it that hard for me
to get a classroom?

849
00:34:15,921 --> 00:34:16,927
That's not the hard part.

850
00:34:17,441 --> 00:34:19,520
The hard part is to pacify the people.

851
00:34:20,240 --> 00:34:21,720
You see, if I'm giving you
what you want now,

852
00:34:22,040 --> 00:34:23,040
what should I do

853
00:34:23,480 --> 00:34:24,480
when other people ask me
for the same thing?

854
00:34:25,080 --> 00:34:26,601
If I don't give it to them,
I'll be biased.

855
00:34:26,921 --> 00:34:28,361
(You and I are from the same sect.)

856
00:34:28,520 --> 00:34:29,841
(Just one report letter)

857
00:34:29,961 --> 00:34:31,121
(is enough to land me in trouble.)

858
00:34:31,720 --> 00:34:33,078
I thought you promised

859
00:34:33,161 --> 00:34:34,201
Fellow Zhang

860
00:34:34,401 --> 00:34:35,878
that your academy would help us out

861
00:34:35,961 --> 00:34:37,278
if we were in trouble?

862
00:34:37,361 --> 00:34:39,358
Now, the apprentice class
is in a pickle here.

863
00:34:39,441 --> 00:34:40,601
How do you plan to resolve the issue?

864
00:34:42,562 --> 00:34:43,562
Me?

865
00:34:45,921 --> 00:34:47,157
At most, I can hold one,

866
00:34:47,240 --> 00:34:48,240
two,

867
00:34:48,530 --> 00:34:49,530
or even three seminars for you.

868
00:34:50,000 --> 00:34:52,280
(But now, you're asking me
for a classroom.)

869
00:34:52,520 --> 00:34:53,878
And, you'll be using it
for quite a few years.

870
00:34:53,961 --> 00:34:55,401
The thing is,
you're not paying rent for it.

871
00:34:56,121 --> 00:34:57,881
How can I explain myself
to the higher-ups?

872
00:35:00,841 --> 00:35:01,841
What about this?

873
00:35:02,393 --> 00:35:03,873
For the sake of your apprentice class,

874
00:35:04,441 --> 00:35:07,480
I'll sacrifice my career.

875
00:35:08,080 --> 00:35:09,681
I'll resign

876
00:35:10,121 --> 00:35:11,520
(and be the class teacher)

877
00:35:11,760 --> 00:35:13,040
(for the apprentice class.)

878
00:35:13,201 --> 00:35:16,601
I'll be thick-skinned and go out
to ask for donations.

879
00:35:17,401 --> 00:35:18,401
What do you think?

880
00:35:18,506 --> 00:35:19,506
Stop your pointless chatter.

881
00:35:21,266 --> 00:35:22,266
Fine.

882
00:35:22,961 --> 00:35:23,961
I'll think of something myself.

883
00:35:43,601 --> 00:35:45,441
Your lot

884
00:35:45,560 --> 00:35:49,720
is the best out of all.

885
00:35:50,240 --> 00:35:51,520
That's all?

886
00:35:53,641 --> 00:35:55,637
Is this a good thing or a bad thing?

887
00:35:55,720 --> 00:35:57,441
-I didn't get it.
-Yeah. Tell us the details.

888
00:35:57,601 --> 00:36:00,320
-Is it good or bad?
-Late bloomer.

889
00:36:01,361 --> 00:36:03,401
How late is late?

890
00:36:03,921 --> 00:36:09,280
According to how
modern people calculate age,

891
00:36:09,921 --> 00:36:12,080
it'll be around 60 years old.

892
00:36:15,040 --> 00:36:16,040
60 years old?

893
00:36:16,800 --> 00:36:18,080
That's pretty good.

894
00:36:18,320 --> 00:36:19,358
People always seek out

895
00:36:19,441 --> 00:36:20,798
senior TCM practitioners.

896
00:36:20,881 --> 00:36:24,467
That's not it. Both of my parents made
a name for themselves at a young age.

897
00:36:24,551 --> 00:36:26,878
But I'm only making a name for myself
at 60? Do you think that's appropriate?

898
00:36:26,962 --> 00:36:30,203
Yeah. Why not? I think it's good
enough to make a name for yourself.

899
00:36:30,361 --> 00:36:31,397
Look at me.

900
00:36:31,480 --> 00:36:32,800
I'll stay like this
for the rest of my life.

901
00:36:33,041 --> 00:36:34,878
I'm the same even when I'm 80.

902
00:36:34,961 --> 00:36:36,000
Are you trying

903
00:36:36,418 --> 00:36:37,418
to console me?

904
00:36:40,201 --> 00:36:41,201
I don't think so.

905
00:36:44,601 --> 00:36:46,441
Let's check out the other stalls.

906
00:36:46,641 --> 00:36:47,641
Alright.

907
00:36:47,825 --> 00:36:49,264
-Let's check them out.
-They're selling food.

908
00:36:49,777 --> 00:36:50,857
-Meng Meng, let's go.
-Let's go.

909
00:36:51,018 --> 00:36:52,018
Let's go.

910
00:37:00,641 --> 00:37:01,641
Excuse me.

911
00:37:02,201 --> 00:37:03,201
Let me ask you something.

912
00:37:03,680 --> 00:37:05,721
Are you a human or a robot?

913
00:37:06,441 --> 00:37:09,961
Sir, what other questions do you have?

914
00:37:10,873 --> 00:37:12,353
It's fine. Thank you.

915
00:37:17,533 --> 00:37:18,756
One of them

916
00:37:18,840 --> 00:37:20,080
is a late bloomer

917
00:37:20,280 --> 00:37:21,441
while the other one is a prodigy.

918
00:37:31,560 --> 00:37:32,961
What should we do now?

919
00:37:33,720 --> 00:37:34,760
I just feel apologetic

920
00:37:35,040 --> 00:37:36,560
toward Ms Dong.

921
00:37:37,040 --> 00:37:39,560
You always led a reclusive life.

922
00:37:39,961 --> 00:37:40,961
Now,

923
00:37:41,529 --> 00:37:42,849
you're here.

924
00:37:43,161 --> 00:37:45,237
But we don't even have a classroom
for you to teach them.

925
00:37:45,320 --> 00:37:46,800
Yeah, it's all my fault.

926
00:37:47,601 --> 00:37:48,961
I should've expected this to happen

927
00:37:49,161 --> 00:37:51,841
when I severed my ties
with them.

928
00:37:52,401 --> 00:37:53,401
Actually, they're not obliged

929
00:37:53,633 --> 00:37:54,913
to help us out

930
00:37:55,089 --> 00:37:56,569
for free.

931
00:37:57,066 --> 00:37:58,185
Businessmen

932
00:37:58,648 --> 00:38:01,057
value profit over righteousness.

933
00:38:01,785 --> 00:38:02,957
That's a hasty generalization.

934
00:38:05,040 --> 00:38:07,359
There are many
righteous businessmen too.

935
00:38:08,800 --> 00:38:09,920
Master,

936
00:38:10,176 --> 00:38:11,777
you always told me

937
00:38:12,040 --> 00:38:13,441
that if I have an idea,

938
00:38:13,560 --> 00:38:14,800
everything will fall into place.

939
00:38:15,080 --> 00:38:16,080
I had this idea

940
00:38:16,601 --> 00:38:17,641
for a long time.

941
00:38:17,921 --> 00:38:19,038
Why isn't anyone

942
00:38:19,121 --> 00:38:20,681
giving me a classroom?

943
00:38:21,161 --> 00:38:22,397
You see,

944
00:38:22,480 --> 00:38:23,841
that only works

945
00:38:24,201 --> 00:38:25,201
when you're Buddha.

946
00:38:26,040 --> 00:38:27,197
You still have a long way to go.

947
00:38:27,280 --> 00:38:28,280
You're right.

948
00:38:29,601 --> 00:38:30,681
You see,

949
00:38:31,208 --> 00:38:32,609
knowledge and action
should go hand in hand.

950
00:38:33,441 --> 00:38:35,760
From realising
the righteousness of the event

951
00:38:36,000 --> 00:38:37,518
to the completion of the event,

952
00:38:37,601 --> 00:38:38,601
everything else in between

953
00:38:38,720 --> 00:38:40,240
acts as your trial.

954
00:38:41,641 --> 00:38:44,121
God is giving you an ordeal

955
00:38:44,361 --> 00:38:46,121
called The Dignity Ordeal.

956
00:38:48,601 --> 00:38:49,641
Master, you're right.

957
00:38:51,641 --> 00:38:53,358
Master, I'll be honest with you.

958
00:38:53,441 --> 00:38:55,280
In the past, I didn't think

959
00:38:56,000 --> 00:38:57,280
that this industry was that tough.

960
00:38:58,000 --> 00:38:59,201
But now, it's...

961
00:39:01,520 --> 00:39:02,520
Think about it.

962
00:39:03,401 --> 00:39:04,881
Throughout your career,

963
00:39:05,681 --> 00:39:06,681
you were talented

964
00:39:07,401 --> 00:39:08,997
and you had academic qualifications.

965
00:39:09,080 --> 00:39:10,080
And,

966
00:39:10,240 --> 00:39:11,758
you had elders like us

967
00:39:11,841 --> 00:39:12,961
backing you up.

968
00:39:13,361 --> 00:39:15,120
Of course you had a smooth journey.

969
00:39:15,200 --> 00:39:16,440
You're right.

970
00:39:16,520 --> 00:39:17,676
Now,

971
00:39:17,760 --> 00:39:20,040
I'm old.

972
00:39:20,441 --> 00:39:22,361
I'm afraid I won't be able
to back you up anymore.

973
00:39:22,841 --> 00:39:24,121
I'm afraid you need to back me up

974
00:39:24,961 --> 00:39:27,121
in the future.

975
00:39:28,441 --> 00:39:30,841
Dad, such chatter is meaningless.

976
00:39:31,520 --> 00:39:32,917
Now, we need to figure out a way

977
00:39:33,000 --> 00:39:34,401
to resolve this issue.

978
00:39:34,681 --> 00:39:39,039
Yeah.
Ms Dong,

979
00:39:39,122 --> 00:39:40,358
I'm truly sorry.

980
00:39:40,441 --> 00:39:42,441
We invited you all the way here,

981
00:39:42,681 --> 00:39:43,681
however,

982
00:39:43,841 --> 00:39:45,358
we don't even have a place

983
00:39:45,441 --> 00:39:46,641
for you to teach them.

984
00:39:46,921 --> 00:39:47,921
That's fine.

985
00:39:49,401 --> 00:39:50,401
When we decide

986
00:39:51,681 --> 00:39:53,401
to take the righteous path,

987
00:39:54,000 --> 00:39:55,320
we have to put in much more effort

988
00:39:55,480 --> 00:39:57,720
than taking the back door.

989
00:39:58,601 --> 00:39:59,677
God will test you

990
00:39:59,760 --> 00:40:00,961
repeatedly

991
00:40:01,587 --> 00:40:02,867
to see

992
00:40:03,747 --> 00:40:05,626
whether you're truly sincere
in taking this path.

993
00:40:07,592 --> 00:40:08,592
If you can pass God's test

994
00:40:09,000 --> 00:40:10,560
every time without changing your goal,

995
00:40:11,121 --> 00:40:13,000
you'll achieve what you wish for.

996
00:40:15,641 --> 00:40:16,641
In my opinion,

997
00:40:17,000 --> 00:40:18,000
this isn't even

998
00:40:18,280 --> 00:40:19,720
an ordeal for you.

999
00:40:20,720 --> 00:40:23,000
You're an academician.

1000
00:40:23,340 --> 00:40:25,459
You published books and
made a name for yourself.

1001
00:40:27,040 --> 00:40:28,280
But people like us?

1002
00:40:28,800 --> 00:40:29,841
It's quite difficult for us

1003
00:40:30,760 --> 00:40:32,641
to pass our legacy
to the next generation.

1004
00:40:34,000 --> 00:40:35,361
In Taoism,

1005
00:40:35,641 --> 00:40:36,841
masters will look for
their own disciples.

1006
00:40:37,760 --> 00:40:39,441
I agreed to join your class

1007
00:40:39,961 --> 00:40:41,441
not because to help you out.

1008
00:40:42,000 --> 00:40:43,520
I'm helping myself out.

1009
00:40:44,465 --> 00:40:45,465
I was thinking

1010
00:40:45,593 --> 00:40:46,593
that I'll encounter a disciple

1011
00:40:47,050 --> 00:40:49,209
who's a kindred spirit
if I teach enough classes.

1012
00:40:50,240 --> 00:40:51,740
Maybe that person is willing
to inherit our legacy

1013
00:40:52,720 --> 00:40:55,080
without changing anything.

1014
